#
# how to add a whole directory into a project
#
open Visual Studio 2015 Community
open the project
drop the whole directory from Windows Explorer into the project in the Solution Explorer into VS,
click Show All Files at the top of Solution Explorer
click the whole directory, right-click, click Include in Project.
=> a + symbol is shown.
=> Done.

